race.comment: MY FRIEND BEC (3) boasts a strong record this journey here with eight wins and two minors from 12 tries. Missed the frame latest (23.64) when sixth over 401m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Expected to be in the finish. MIDNIGHT FURY (8) boasts a strong record this course with five wins and two minors from 10 tries. Placed last time (18.38) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 0.8 lengths. Looks one of the chances. JENNIFER JUNIPER (1) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (18.90) last time in a Mix 3/4 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Can measure up this time. SWAN'S SPIRIT (4) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.
